definition.edge_share_rank: rank over GF(2) of incidence matrix A_ij with A_ij[t,u]=1 iff triangles share an edge (2 common vertices).
definition.intersection_pair_rank: rank over GF(2) of matrix C_ij with C_ij[t,u]= <[∂t],[∂u]> where <.,.> is the mod-2 intersection form on H1 induced from simplicial cup product.
